subject: roll-on sunscreen
body:
garlic chicken musubi

went to a really nice beach

roll-on sunscreen, my preferred form of sunscreen

every time i have applied sunscreen to myself this trip in my head i hear the beat of "public service announcement" but instead of "music biz number one supplier" my brain autocompletes "sunscreen biz number one applier"

when the people who are next to me on the beach are not playing keep it up with a volleyball
